				NumSamples numpix div 0.5 gt
				{
					/numsteps numpix 2 div round cvi dup 1 le{pop 2}if def
					/rampIndxInc NumSamples 1 sub numsteps div def
					/subsampling true def
				}if
			}if
			ext0
			{
				0 getrampcolor
				xMin xStart lt
